<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terms of Service - BroqInsta Utility Governance</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <meta name="description" content="BroqInsta terms of service - service scope, usage limitations, and liability disclaimer.">
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= siteUrl %>/terms">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Terms of Service - BroqInsta Utility Governance">
    <meta property="og:description" content="BroqInsta terms of service - service scope, usage limitations, and liability disclaimer.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="<%= siteUrl %>/images/preview.png">
    <meta property="og:url" content="<%= siteUrl %>/terms">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="BroqInsta">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Terms of Service - BroqInsta Utility Governance">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="BroqInsta terms of service - service scope, usage limitations, and liability disclaimer.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= siteUrl %>/images/preview.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <script src="/js/tailwind.js"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-[#FAFBFC] min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-4 py-24 max-w-4xl">
        <nav class="mb-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
            <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList">
                <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
                    <a href="/" itemprop="item" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors"><span itemprop="name">Home</span></a>
                    <meta itemprop="position" content="1">
                </li>
                <li><span class="mx-2">/</span></li>
                <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
                    <span itemprop="name" class="text-gray-600">Terms of Service</span>
                    <meta itemprop="position" content="2">
                </li>
            </ol>
        </nav>

        <div class="glass-card p-12 md:p-20 rounded-[3rem] animate-on-scroll">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-12 italic">Terms of Utility.</h1>
            <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">01. Service
                        Scope</h2>
                    <p>BroqInsta provides a technical extraction utility for educational and backup purposes. By using
                        this service, you agree to respect the intellectual property rights of content creators.</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">02. Usage
                        Limitations</h2>
                    <p>Users are prohibited from using BroqInsta for mass data harvesting or automated scraping. Abuse
                        of our bandwidth may result in temporary session termination.</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">03. Liability
                        Disclaimer</h2>
                    <p>BroqInsta is provided "as-is" without warranty. We do not host any of the media extracted; we
                        simply provide a secure relay to publicly available content.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>